            <ObservedData>
              <Attribute Type="Description">In an affected male from a family with Billuart-type X-linked syndromic intellectual developmental disorder (MRXSBL; 300486), originally designated MRX60, Billuart et al. (1998) detected a 1-bp deletion (1578del) within the valine-526 codon in the OPHN1 gene. RT-PCR analysis using RNA isolated from a lymphoblastoid cell line from the proband showed that the mutation resulted in a barely detectable amount of the oligophrenin-1 transcript. Cosegregation of this frameshift mutation with the disease was confirmed in the large family. The frameshift mutation was not detected in 100 control individuals.</Attribute>
